<headline>Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued June 25 at 9:04PM CDT until June 26 at 12:00AM CDT by NWS Saint Louis</headline>
<description>SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH 410 REMAINS VALID UNTIL MIDNIGHT CDT
TONIGHT FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS
IN ILLINOIS THIS WATCH INCLUDES 11 COUNTIES
IN SOUTH CENTRAL ILLINOIS
BOND                  FAYETTE               MONTGOMERY
IN SOUTHWEST ILLINOIS
CALHOUN               GREENE                JERSEY
MACOUPIN              MADISON
IN WEST CENTRAL ILLINOIS
ADAMS                 BROWN                 PIKE
IN MISSOURI THIS WATCH INCLUDES 7 COUNTIES
IN EAST CENTRAL MISSOURI
LINCOLN               MONTGOMERY            SAINT CHARLES
SAINT LOUIS           SAINT LOUIS CITY      WARREN
IN NORTHEAST MISSOURI
PIKE
THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF ALTON, BOWLING GREEN, EDWARDSVILLE,
LITCHFIELD, MOUNT STERLING, PITTSFIELD, QUINCY, SAINT CHARLES,
SAINT LOUIS, AND VANDALIA.</description>
